  "notes": "The NYC internet microgenre, not 2009 LA jerkin'. The marker is the snare: staggered and clustered, displaced off-grid around where the backbeat should be, with stop-start gaps. Kicks borrow Jersey-club 3-3-2 groupings. Alone among these genres it wants its timing randomised rather than tightened — the 'off' quantization is the aesthetic.",

